            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609339499&amp;ssig=EgCpyoGc0o" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

        <div class="WB_detail">

                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E8%87%B360%25%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%23&amp;from=default">#国内口罩产能恢复至60%左右#</a>】工信部消费品工业司副司长曹学军2日在工信部新闻发布会上回答记者提问时称，目前全国口罩产能恢复至60%左右，但与实际需求相比还有较大缺口。工信部全力组织国内重点物资企业复产复工，同时紧急协调用好按日、美、欧标准加工用于出口等医疗物资，加大国际采购，竭尽全 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IsjhibQ5R" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467472922821859:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467472922821859&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                <a name="4467470578590063" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IsjdvA2Fp?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-02 10:44" date="1580611450000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467470578590063:fromprofile"> 2月2日 10:44</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

                                <a name="4467462072630771" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IsiZNb2nN?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-02 10:10" date="1580609422000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467462072630771:fromprofile"> 2月2日 10:10</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%2388%E5%B2%81%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E6%8A%8A%E5%AD%98%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%843%E4%B8%87%E6%8D%90%E7%BB%99%E6%88%98%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%BF%23&amp;from=default">#88岁老兵把存下的3万捐给战疫一线#</a>：国家有难我分担！】呼和浩特88岁老人高治邦，是一名退伍老兵，曾在战场上救护伤员。几日前，老人通过电视新闻得知疫情严重，将自己省吃俭用攒下的3万元捐了出来，表示一定要为抗击疫情贡献微薄力量。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a><a title="88岁老兵在抗击疫情中再现英雄本色" href="http://t.cn/A6POA3Jy" alt="http://t.cn/A6POA3Jy" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_link">O</i>88岁老兵在抗击疫情中再现英雄本色</a> <a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%91%E5%86%85%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E9%A2%91%E9%81%93?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民网内蒙古频道">@人民网内蒙古频道</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%90%89%E6%9E%97%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E6%E4%BE%8B%E7%B4%AF%E8%AE%A123%E4%BE%8B%23&amp;from=default">#吉林新增6例累计23例#</a>】2月1日0-24时，吉林新增确诊病例6例，均为长春市报告，其中2例为东丰县转诊病例。截至2月1日24时，吉林累计报告确诊病例23例，长春市治愈出院1例，现在院隔离治疗确诊病例22例。其中长春市12例，吉林市3例，延边州2例，松原市2例，通化市1例，四平市1例， ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IsiKL9blg" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467452752188554:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467452752188554&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609339508&amp;ssig=jvDrZ2ZOg5" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609339515&amp;ssig=A9vcLBPAaB" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【国家卫健委：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E5%90%8E%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%B1%E8%BF%91%E7%81%AB%E5%8C%96%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎患者死亡后应就近火化#</a> 不得移运】国家卫健委发布了《新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎患者遗体置工作指引（试行）》，其中明确提出，遗体应当就近全部火化，不得采用埋葬或其它保存遗体方式，不得移运。新冠肺炎患者死亡后，不得举行遗体告别仪式和利用遗体进行其它形式的丧葬活动。 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/Isiqlir6A" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467440094394100:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467440094394100&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%2331%E4%B8%AA%E7%9C%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%B8%82%E7%B4%AF%E8%AE%A1%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E5%87%BA%E9%99%A2328%E4%BE%8B%23&amp;from=default">#31个省区市累计治愈出院328例#</a>】截至2月1日24时，国家卫生健康委收到31个省（自治区、直辖市）和新疆生产建设兵团累计报告确诊病例14380例，现有重症病例2110例，累计死亡病例304例，累计治愈出院病例328例，共有疑似病例19544例。 ​​​​                                            </div>

                    <div class="WB_media_wrap clearfix" node-type="feed_list_media_prev">
        <div class="media_box">
            <!--判断图片的个数，渲染图片-->

                                                                                 【<a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" suda-uatrack=\"key=topic_click&value=click_topic\" class=\"a_topic\"
